has%20really%20caught%20the%20attention%20of%20all%20of%20these%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20big%2C%20powerful%20G20%20nations%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20it%20is%20the%20vision%20of%20PM%20Modi%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20said%20the%20ambition%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20is%20to%20intensify%20the%20digitalisation%20of%20the%20governance%20process%20and%20expand%20the%20DPI%20framework%20to%20cover%20almost%20all%20public%20services.%20He%20said%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20widen%20and%20expand%20the%20innovation%20ecosystem%20that%20supports%20and%20takes%20DPI%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20you%20are%20a%20bitter%20opponent%20of%20the%20government%2C%20you%20cannot%20but%20accept%20and%20acknowledge%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20are%20countries%20around%20the%20world%20that%20are%20lining%20up%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20to%20say%20can%20we%20also%20take%20this%20open-source%2C%20very%20flexible%2C%20very%20innovative%20India%20Stack%2C%20India%20DPI%20and%20implement%20it%20in%20our%20countries%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20asserted%20that%20India%20is%20turning%20on%20its%20head%20the%20narrative%20about%20technology%20being%20very%20expensive%2C%20very%20exclusionary%2C%20that%20only%20the%20very%20rich%20countries%20can%20afford%20the%20luxury%20of%20digitalisation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20see%20what%20the%20United%20Payments%20Interface%20(UPI)%20is%2C%20it%20is%20a%20solution%20to%20solve%20a%20pressing%20use%20case%20of%20the%20government.%20For%20many%20years%2C%20people%20looked%20at%20India%20and%20said%20Rs%20100%20leaves%20Delhi%20and%20Rs%2015%20reaches%20the%20beneficiary%20because%20the%20whole%20process%2C%20the%20government%20pipe%2C%20is%20so%20leaky%20and%20corroded%20that%20there%20is%20so%20much%20of%20corruption%20and%20leakage%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20solve%20that%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20came%20up%20with%20the%20Jan%20Dhan%20Yojana%2C%20direct%20benefit%20transfer%20and%20then%20you%20had%20UPI%20evolve.%20So%2C%20just%20understand%20that%20you%20had%20governance%20problems%20being%20solved%20and%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20you%20have%20this%20vibrant%20innovation%20ecosystem%2C%20which%20has%20now%20become%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20biggest%20fintech%20innovation%20ecosystems%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Bill%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20stop%20platforms%20from%20misusing%20Indians'%20personal%20data%20and%20to%20address%20the%20%E2%80%9Casymmetry%E2%80%9D%20between%20the%20citizen%20and%20the%20platform.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20powers%20the%20bill%20gives%20to%20the%20government%20and%20the%20privacy%20issues%20it%20raises%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20powers%20are%20in%20very%20narrowly%20defined%20circumstances%20of%20emergencies.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20national%20security%20incident%2C%20you%20don't%20certainly%20expect%20the%20government%20to%20go%20to%20suspected%20terrorists%20and%20say%20can%20you%20give%20me%20your%20consent%20for%20your%20personal%20data.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20went%20on%20to%20cite%20examples%20of%20pandemics%20and%20natural%20disasters%20and%20said%20the%20exemptions%20are%20for%20legitimate%20purposes.%20The%20minister%20said%20every%20fundamental%20right%20has%20reasonable%20restrictions%20and%20that%20applies%20to%20privacy%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693039560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fke18j5s_rajeev-chandrasekhar-650_650x400_26_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwant-to-intensify-digitisation-of-governance-rajeev-chandrasekhar-to-ndtv-4331310%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22