%20human%20activities.%20If%20everything%20goes%20perfect%2C%20then%20we%20can%20have%20a%20go-ahead%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20narrated%20the%20relief%20they%20felt%20when%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20lander%20finally%20touched%20down%20near%20the%20Moon's%20south%20pole.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20have%20been%20very%20closely%20associated%20with%20the%20ISRO%20team%2C%20we%20nervous.%20My%20first%20nervous%20moment%20was%20when%20the%20Chandrayaan-3%20craft%20left%20Earth's%20orbit%20for%20the%20Moon's%20orbit...%20The%20landing%20was%20so%20smooth%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Moon%20landing%20was%20a%20quantum%20jump%20in%20the%20journey%20of%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20and%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20happened%20because%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20threw%20open%20the%20space%20sector.%20Till%20about%202019%2C%20the%20gates%20of%20Sriharikota%20were%20closed%2C%20but%20this%20time%20the%20media%20and%20schoolchildren%20were%20invited.%20It%20was%20owned%20by%20the%20people%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said%2C%20adding%20the%20funding%20for%20the%20space%20programme%20has%20been%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20the%20first%20nation%20to%20land%20a%20spacecraft%20near%20the%20Moon's%20south%20pole%2C%20and%20the%20fourth%20nation%20to%20send%20a%20lander%20to%20the%20Moon%20successfully%20after%20the%20erstwhile%20USSR%2C%20the%20US%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693038120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fs0r2m5h_jitendra-singh-650_650x400_26_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffemale-robot-vyommitra-will-go-to-space-science-minister-on-gaganyaan-4331391%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20will%20send%20a%20female%20robot%20%26quot%3BVyommitra%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Gaganyaan%20missio