%2FBreakfast-scheme-in-Chennai-2-750x500-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20extended%20its%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20Breakfast%20Scheme%20for%20primary%20students%20to%2029%2C463%20more%20schools%20on%20Friday%2C%20August%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scheme%20will%20now%20serve%20nutritious%20breakfast%20to%2017%20lakh%20students%20from%20Classes%20I%20to%20V%20studying%20in%2031%2C008%20schools%20at%20an%20annual%20cost%20of%20Rs%20404.41%20crore.%20Launched%20on%20September%2015%2C%202022%2C%20the%20scheme%20initially%20covered%201%2C14%2C095%20students%20in%201%2C545%20schools%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%2033.56%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%20launched%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20scheme%20at%20Tirukkuvalai%20in%20Nagapattinam%2C%20where%20his%20father%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20M.%20Karunanidhi%20had%20studied.%20Stalin%20also%20shared%20the%20meal%20with%20the%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20expanded%20the%20scheme%20considering%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20preliminary%20phase%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20government%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20aim%20is%20to%20ensure%20children%20attend%20school%20without%20hunger%20and%C2%A0prevent%20malnutrition%2C%20achieve%20average%20height%20in%20children%2C%20prevent%20underweight%20in%20adolescents%2C%20prevent%20anemia%20and%20vitamin%20B12%20deficiency.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStalin%20had%20invited%20elected%20representatives%20to%20launch%20the%20plan%E2%80%99s%20extension%20in%20a%20government%20primary%20school%20in%20their%20respective%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EVIDEO%20%7C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20CM%20MK%20Stalin%20enjoys%20a%20meal%20with%20school%20children%20in%20Nagapattinam%20district%20as%20he%20launched%20the%20Chief%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20breakfast%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20s