B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BDigital%20Transformation%2C%20Infrastructure%20Our%20Priorities%26quot%3B%3A%20G20%20Sherpa%20Amitabh%20Kant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia's%20G20%20Sherpa%20Amitabh%20Kant%20laid%20out%20a%20positive%2C%20ambitious%20agenda%20for%20the%20country's%20presidency%20of%20the%20prestigious%20grouping%20and%20said%20that%20while%20the%20world%20is%20full%20of%20challenges%2C%20India%20sees%20them%20as%20an%20opportunity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelivering%20the%20Keynote%20Address%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspecial.ndtv.com%2Fdecoding-g20-ndtv-conclave-121%2F%5C%22%3ENDTV%20Conclave%3C%2Fa%3E%20today%2C%20Mr%20Kant%20said%20India's%20priorities%20during%20its%20presidency%20and%20the%20G20%20meeting%20next%20month%20will%20be%20a%20focus%20on%20digital%20transformation%2C%20infrastructure%20building%20and%20women-led%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDuring%20G20%2C%20our%20ambition%2C%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20said%2C%20is%20to%20be%20inclusive%2C%20decisive%2C%20ambitious%2C%20and%20action-oriented.%20In%20most%20countries%2C%20the%20G20%20is%20held%20in%20one%20city%2C%20or%20two%20cities.%20Unlike%20the%20football%20world%20cup%20in%20Qatar%20or%20the%20cricket%20world%20cup%2C%20G20%20is%20through%20the%20year.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20used%20this%20opportunity%20to%20take%20G20%20out%20into%20every%20single%20state%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20G20%20Sherpa%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kant%20said%20India%20has%20covered%20over%2060%20cities%20and%20used%20this%20opportunity%20to%20improve%20infrastructure%20in%20those%20places.%20%26quot%3BEvery%20single%20citizen%20of%20India%20was%20involved%20in%20G20%20in%20some%20manner%20or%20the%20other%20and%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20foreign%20policy%20and%20diplomacy%20reached%20every%20single%20household%20of%20India.%20The%20presidency%20is%20being%20hosted%20at%20a%20time%20when%20India%20is%20the%20fifth-largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20third-largest%20economy%20by%202027%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20out%20some%20of%20India's%20achievements%2C%20Mr%20Kant%20said%20a%20lot%20had%20been%20done%20in%20the%20last%20seven%20to%20eight%20years.%20%E2%80%9CWe've%20built%20about%2040%20million%20houses%2C%20which%20is%20like%20making%20a%20house%20for%20every%20Australian.%20We've%20made%20about%20110%20million%20toilets%2C%20which%20is%20like%20making%20a%20toilet%20for%20every%20single%20citizen%20of%20Germany.%20We%20have%20provided%20223%20million%20piped%20water%20connections%2C%20which%20is%20like%20providing%20a%20water%20connection%20to%20every%20citizen%20of%20Brazil%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20made%2055%2C000%20km%20of%20road.%20And%2C%20during%20the%20Covid%20period%2C%20we%20have%20provided%20Covid%20vaccination%2C%20almost%20paperless%2C%20to%202.2%20billion%20people%20of%20India%E2%80%A6%20As%20the%20Bank%20of%20International%20Settlements%20has%20said%2C%20the%20digital%20transformation%20story%20of%20India%2C%20we%20do%20about%2046%25%20of%20the%20real%20fast%20time%20payments%20in%20the%20world.%20We%20do%2011x%20of%20what%20USA%20and%20Europe%20do%2C%20we%20do%204x%20of%20what%20China%20does.%20What%20we%20have%20achieved%20in%20seven%20years%20is%20equivalent%20to%20what%20India%20would%20have%20achieved%20in%2050%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20India's%20priorities%20for%20the%20G20%2C%20the%20Sherpa%20said%20the%20first%20is%20that%20the%20world%20must%20have%20strong%2C%20sustained%2C%20balanced%20and%20inclusive%20growth.%20The%20second%20is%20to%20accelerate%20the%20pace%20of%20Sustainable%20Development%20Goals%2C%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20only%2012%20of%20the%20169%20SDGs%20are%20on%20track%20right%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20is%20climate%20action%20and%20climate%20finance%2C%20Mr%20Kant%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20world%20may%20survive%2C%20but%20we%20will%20all%20go%20extinct%20if%20we%20don't%20live%20up%20to%20the%20promise%20of%20limiting%20global%20temperature%20rise%20to%201.5-degree%20Celsius.%20Pointing%20to%20the%20need%20for%20long-term%20finance%20for%20all%20of%20this%2C%20he%20said%20the%20fourth%20priority%20was%20the%20redesign%20and%20reformulation%20of%20multilateral%20financial%20institutions%20set%20up%20after%20World%20War%20II.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThen%2C%20our%20priority%20is%20technological%20transformation%20and%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%2C%20which%20India%20has%20built%20up.%20If%20you%20look%20around%20the%20world%2C%20four%20billion%20people%20do%20not%20have%20a%20digital%20identity%2C%20three%20billion%20people%20do%20not%20have%20a%20bank%20account.%20Another%20priority%20of%20our%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20been%20women-led%20development.%20Women%20have%20to%20be%20put%20into%20positions%20of%20leadership%20so%20that%20we%20can%20enhance%20their%20learning%20outcomes%2C%20improve%20their%20health%20standards%20and%20break%20this%20vicious%20cycle%20of%20malnutrition%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Mr%20Kant.%C2%A0%5Cn%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22NDTV%20G20%20Conclave%20-%20watch%20live%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fspecial.ndtv.com%2Fdecoding-g20-ndtv-conclave-121%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22g20%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fdecoding20-1200x738.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20G20%20Sherpa%20said%20India%20has%20focused%20on%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20which%20has%20a%20young%20population%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20drive%20growth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20look%20forward%20to%20the%20G20%20leaders'%20summit.%20Negotiations%20for%20the%20leaders'%20statement%20are%20on.%20Every%20word%20is%20hotly%20contested%2C%20it%20is%20debated%20between%2020%20countries.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20