nt%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-when-randeep-hooda-spoke-about-his-breakup-with-sushmita-sen-i-gave-it-too-much-time-in-life%2Farticleshow%2F103053814.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Former%20ISRO%20Chief%20Explains%20What%20Chandrayaan-3%20Success%20Means%20For%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20has%20pushed%20India%20into%20the%20front%20row%20of%20space-faring%20nations%2C%20which%20means%20the%20country%20will%20now%20also%20have%20a%20say%20in%20the%20exploration%20of%20outer%20space%20and%20use%20of%20pace%20resources%2C%20Former%20ISRO%20Chairman%20K%20Kasturirangan%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20science%2C%20low%20cost%26quot%3B%20approach%20of%20ISRO%20has%20helped%20design%20the%20nation's%20space%20programmes%20in%20a%20cost-effective%2C%20but%20innovative%20ways.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20developing%20countries%20too%20must%20invest%20in%20space%20programmes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20Kasturirangan%2C%20during%20whose%20tenure%20as%20ISRO%20chairman%20the%20moon%20missions%20were%20planned%2C%20said%20India%20now%20has%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bhigh-table%26quot%3B%20in%20deciding%20matters%20related%20to%20space%20exploration%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInternational%20regimes%20in%20the%20past%20have%20shut%20others%20from%20space%20pursuits%2C%20particularly%20with%20regard%20to%20adopting%20emerging%20technologies%20and%20in%20that%20context%2C%20India%20has%20to%20invest%20in%20space%20exploration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20nation%20is%20looking%20at%20taking%20up%20technologies%20that%20are%20opening%20up%20new%20frontiers%2C%20the%20problem%20is%20some%20nations%20-%20that%20have%20already%20mastered%20it%20-%20don't%20want%20the%20other%20nations%20to%20join%20that%20club.%20This%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20nuclear%20energy%20and%20weapons%20club%20too.%20If%20you%20postpone%20such%20programmes%20for%20too%20long%20thinking%20you%20will%20do%20it%20later%2C%20the%20international%20regime%20will%20manipulate%20the%20system%20so%20much%20that%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20for%20you%20to%20enter%2C%20because%20it%20is%20seen%20as%20their%20domain.%20India%20is%20making%20sure%20it%20doesn't%20have%20to%20face%20these%20hindrances.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20new%20technology%2C%20and%20new%20area%20of%20exploration%20and%20investigation%20-%20be%20it%20the%20earth%2C%20or%20ocean%20or%20space%20-%20we%20must%20make%20sure%20we%20showcase%20our%20abilities%20and%20be%20counted%20among%20the%20front%20ranking%20nations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kasturirangan%20said%20countries%20with%20the%20right%20kind%20of%20technology%2C%20necessary%20science%20background%20and%20financial%20resources%20will%20become%20part%20of%20this%20great%20journey.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20cannot%20be%20left%20behind%20in%20the%20area%20of%20space%20which%20is%20becoming%20key%20to%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20success%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20particularly%20important%20because%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20the%20country%20has%20demonstrated%20that%20it%20can%20explore%20parts%20of%20another%20celestial%20body%20-%20in%20terms%20of%20physical%20and%20chemical%20environment%20and%20other%20parameters%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kasturirangan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20very%20important%20capability.%20One%20is%20the%20science%20part%20of%20it%2C%20the%20other%20is%20the%20technology%20part%20of%20it.%20And%20the%20other%20is%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20total%20mission%2C%20be%20it%20the%20orbit%2C%20the%20rocket%2C%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20lander%20and%20rover%20among%20others.%20This%20represents%20a%20totality%20of%20ability%20to%20explore%20a%20planetary%20object.%20India%20is%20doing%20everything%20in%20its%20capability%20to%20show%20it%20has%20the%20necessary%20credentials%20as%20some%20other%20countries%20including%20US%2C%20China%2C%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20we%20have%20landed%20on%20the%20moon%20is%20also%20significant%2C%20as%20it%20is%20a%20location%20with%20a%20promise%20of%20water%2C%20and%20water%20is%20a%20very%20critical%20element.%26quot%3B%20A%202021%20PWC%20report%20appraised%20the%20lunar%20economy%20at%20a%20promising%20%24170%20billion%20with%20the%20potential%20of%20exponential%20growth%2C%20focussing%20on%20transportation%2C%20lunar%20data%2C%20and%20in%20situ%20resources%20utilisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20signed%20the%20Artemis%20Accords%20(a%20practical%20set%20of%20principles%20to%20guide%20space%20exploration%20cooperation%20among%20nations%2C%20including%20those%20participating%20in%20NASA's%20Artemis%20program)%20that%20gives%20India%20a%20position%20among%20a%20committee%20of%20nations%20of%20using%20lunar%20platforms%20for%20other%20explorations.%20We%20have%20become%20part%20of%20the%20high%20table%20with%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20and%20are%20among%20the%20handful%20of%20nations%20who%20have%20successfully%20demonstrated%20that%20ability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kasturirangan%20said%20apart%20from%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20developing%20countries%20must%20invest%20in%20space%20and%20science%20programmes%20too.%20%26quot%3BOne%20can%20look%20at%20this%20from%20two%20sides%20-%20you%20can%20invest%20in%20a%20welfare%20programme%20and%20still%20be%20finding%20solutions%20for%20it%2075%20years%20later.%20The%20money%20we%20are%20currently%20spending%20on%20space%20is%20not%20anywhere%20close%20to%20what%20many%20of%20the%20other%20countries%20are%20spendin.%20The%20space%20programmes%20we%20do%20are%20really%20cost-effective.%20So%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20building%20Chandrayaan-3%20is%20nothing%20compared%20to%20what%20other%20countries%20have%20spent%20in%20similar%20missions.%20These%20kinds%20of%20space%20programmes%20are%20affordable%2C%20and%20in%20no%20way%20do%20they%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20our%20developmental%20programmes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693030920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fqb5q3jio_chandrayaan-3_625x300_24_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-isro-chief-explains-what-chandrayaan-3-success-means-for-india-4331204%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20success%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%20has%20pushed%20India%20into%20the%20front%20row%20of%20space-faring%20nations%2C%20which%20means%20the%20country%20will%20now%20also%20have%20a%20say%20in%20the%20exploration%20of%20outer%20space%20and%20use%20of%20pace%20resources%2C%20Former%20ISRO%20Chairman%20K%20Kasturirangan%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-isro-chief-explains-what-chandrayaan-3-success-means-for-india-4331204%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-isro-chief-explains-what-chandrayaan-3-success-means-for-india-4331204%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-isro-chief-explains-what-chandrayaan-3-success-means-for-india-4331204%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Boney%20Kapoor%3A%20We%20had%20seen%20rushes%20of%20Dhadak%20when%20Sridevi%20was%20alive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693030823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103071220%2Cimgsize-50916.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fboney-kapoor-we-had-seen-rushes-of-dhadak-when-sridevi-was-alive-she-had-seen-her-daughter-janhvi-kapoor-on-screen-bigi