3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11142639%2FUntitled-design-1-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%2C%20August%2025%2C%20said%20that%20the%20trial%20of%20criminal%20cases%20connected%20with%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20that%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20is%20probing%20can%20be%20conducted%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fmanipur-violence-supreme-court-trial-cbi-cases-assam-statements-virtually%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20top%20court%20said%20victims%20should%20not%20be%20expected%20to%20travel%20to%20Assam%20and%20should%20instead%20be%20facilitated%20to%20provide%20statements%20through%20video%20conferences.%20The%20bench%20led%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20was%20assured%20by%20solicitor%20general%20(SG)%20Tushar%20Mehta%20that%20proper%20internet%20facilities%20shall%20be%20provided%20in%20Manipur%20to%20allow%20statements%20via%20a%20video%20conference.%20However%2C%20those%20who%20wish%20to%20travel%20to%20Guwahati%20to%20appear%20in%20court%20physically%20can%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20you%20want%20the%20statements%20to%20be%20recorded%20in%20Manipur%20and%20not%20in%20Assam%20or%20wherever%20the%20victims%20are%20%E2%80%A6%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Gauhati%20High%20Court%20will%20take%20care%20and%20the%20entire%20process%20will%20be%20done%20virtually%20%E2%80%A6%20We%20will%20not%20ask%20the%20survivor%20to%20travel%20to%20Assam..%20and%20we%20will%20have%20statements%20and%20evidence%20recorded%20in%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%20observed%20orally%20in%20response%20to%20concerns%20raised%20by%20lawyers%20Colin%20Gonsalves%20and%20Vrinda%20Grover%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Senior%20Advocate%20Indira%20Jaising%E2%80%99s%20query%20over%20why%20Assam%20has%20been%20chosen%20for%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20trial%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESG%20Mehta%20said%20that%20Assam%20was%20chosen%20because%20it%20has%20%E2%80%9Cmaximum%E2%80%9D%20internet%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20passed%20some%20directions%20to%20ensure%20a%20fair%20process.%20Among%20these%20was%20asking%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20to%20nominate%20%E2%80%9Cone%20or%20more%20officers%20above%20the%20rank%20of%20Judicial%20Magistrate%20First%20Class%20and%20sessions%20judge%20to%20deal%20with%20such%20trial%20cases%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20that%20judicial%20custody%20shall%20be%20permitted%20in%20Manipur%2C%20while%20the%20recording%20of%20statements%20under%20Section%20164%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC)%20shall%20be%20recorded%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20local%20magistrate%20in%20Manipur.%20The%20acting%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20shall%20designate%20one%20or%20more%20magistrates%20for%20this%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20applications%20for%20the%20production%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20remand%2C%20judicial%20custody%2C%20extension%20of%20custody%2C%20and%20other%20proceedings%20are%20allowed%20to%20be%20conducted%20online%2C%20bearing%20in%20mind%20both%20distance%20and%20security%20issues%20at%20the%20courts%20that%20will%20be%20designated%20to%20conduct%20the%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20said%20that%20the%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20shall%20nominate%20judges%20who%20are%20conversant%20with%20one%20or%20more%20languages%20spoken%20in%20Manipur%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20criminal%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%E2%80%99s%20directions%20came%20during%20a%20hearing%20of%20a%20batch%20of%20pleas%20related%20to%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20in%20Manipur.%20Among%20the%20petitioners%20were%20two%20Kuki%20women%20whose%20assault%20by%20a%20mob%20was%20recorded%20on%20video%20and%20later%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20video%20emerged%2C%20the%20top%20court%20took%20suo%20motu%20cognizance%20of%20the%20matter%20and%20constituted%20an%20all-women%20committee%20%E2%80%93%20headed%20by%20the%20former%20chief%20justice%20of%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20high%20court%20Gita%20Mittal%20%E2%80%93%20to%20suggest%20measures.%20It%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-supreme-court-gita-mittal-committee-report-documents-compensation%5C%22%3Efiled%20three%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20findings%20on%20the%20violence%2C%20suggesting%20recovery%20and%20reconstruction%20of%20documents%20lost%20in%20arson%20and%20gunfire%20and%20just%20compensation%20rules%20and%20the%20appointment%20of%20domain%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEthnic%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20have%20been%20ongoing%20since%20May%203.%20More%20than%20150%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20and%20several%20thousands%20have%20been%20displaced.%20Leaders%20of%20the%20Kuki%20community%20say%20they%20have%20no%20faith%20in%20the%20government%20led%20by%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%20a%20Meitei%2C%20and%20that%20a%20separate%20administration%20for%20the%20Kuki%20tribe%20is%20the%20only%20way%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693027742000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F11142639%2FUntitled-design-1-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanipur-violence-cbi-cases-trial-assam-supreme-court%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20top%20court%20said%20victims%20should%20not%20be%20expected%20to%20travel%20to%20Assam%20and%20should%20instead%20be%20facilitated%20to%20provide%20statements%20through%20video%20conferences.%22%2C%22autho