e%20files%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20has%20been%20continuously%20maintaining%20an%20evasive%20attitude%20toward%20Netaji.%20While%20every%20country%20in%20the%20world%20has%20opened%20up%20all%20Netaji%20files%2C%20Japan%20remains%20the%20only%20country%20to%20keep%20three%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fstill-hidden-after-all-these-years-indias-official-history-of-the-ina-and-japans-netaji-files%5C%22%3Efiles%20on%20Netaji%20%E2%80%98Secret%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20even%20after%2078%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20may%20well%20be%20construed%20as%20an%20indication%20of%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20dubious%20role%20in%20the%20life%20of%20Netaji.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJapan%20has%20the%20answer%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetaji%20was%20last%20seen%20with%20the%20Japanese%20at%20Taihoku.%20In%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20they%20declared%20Netaji%20is%20dead.%C2%A0%20Their%20investigative%20reports%20simply%20confirm%20the%20death.%20They%20do%20not%20say%20what%20led%20to%20the%20crash.%20They%20owe%20an%20explanation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanon%20shot-like%20%E2%80%9Cexplosions%E2%80%9D%20were%20reported%20by%20co-passengers%20Habibur%2C%20Nonogaki%2C%20and%20Takahashi%2C%20before%20the%20plane%20nose-dived.%20Would%20a%20falling%20propeller%20in%20full%20pitch%2C%20as%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20the%20reason%20of%20the%20crash%2C%20give%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdeafening%20noise%E2%80%9D%20inside%20the%20fuselage%3F%C2%A0Was%20it%20really%20a%20cannon%20shell%20that%20hit%20the%20engine%3F%20The%20take-offs%20at%20Saigon%20and%20Tourane%2C%20the%20previous%20halts%2C%20were%20okay.%20Why%20then%20the%20engine%20blew%20off%20at%20Taihoku%20despite%20offloading%20600%20kg%20of%20ammunition%3F%20The%20answers%20may%20lie%20in%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20three%20%E2%80%98Secret%E2%80%99%20files.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20You%20can%20read%20other%20articles%20by%20the%20same%20author%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98mystery%E2%80%99%20