of-gangavaram-port%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emay%20be%20read%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBengaluru%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20is%20in%20a%20hurry.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%20nine%20years%2C%20not%20only%20has%20it%20expanded%20within%20its%20existing%20verticals%20like%20ports%2C%20it%20has%20also%20diversified%20into%20a%20clutch%20of%20new%20businesses%20like%20media%2C%20defence%2C%20drones%2C%20solar%20panel%20manufacturing%20(straddling%20the%20value%20chain%20from%20polysilicon%20to%20solar%20installations)%2C%20electrolysers%2C%20data%20centres%2C%20urban%20renewal%20projects%2C%20airports%20and%20more.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20game%20plan%20brings%20the%20Reliance%20template%20to%20mind.%20Mukesh%20Ambani%20built%20up%20capacity%20and%20then%20signed%20a%20set%20of%20deals%20with%20big%20names%20and%20brought%20his%20debt%20down%20to%20zero.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20Adani%20rapidly%20builds%20a%20network%20of%20assets%20and%20boosts%20its%20market%20capitalisation%20in%20verticals%20like%20ports%2C%20it%20could%20then%20offload%20a%20chunk%20to%20some%20global%20port%20management%20company%2C%20retire%20debts%20with%20the%20proceeds%2C%20and%20become%20a%20zero-debt%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20handful%20of%20interviews%20Gautam%20Adani%20has%20given%2C%20he%20has%20never%20been%20asked%2C%20or%20spoken%2C%20about%20his%20underlying%20strategy%20for%20expansion.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20asked%20the%20Adani%20Group%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20official%20spokesperson%20to%20comment%20on%20this%20characterisation%20of%20its%20business%20plans%20but%20he%20chose%20not%20to%20in%20a%20brief%20response%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E(see%20below)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20our%20questions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChasing%20growth%2C%20the%20group%20has%20relied%20heavily%20on%20%E2%80%98inorganic%20growth%E2%80%99%2C%20acquiring%20concessions%20and%20firms%20to%20rapidly%20add%20scale.%20Apart%20from%20acquisitions%2C%20the%20group%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20big%20gainers%20from%20the%20BJP-led%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fjet-airways-bankruptcy-buying-npa%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edecision%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20create%20a%20bankruptcy%20resolution%20process%20which%2C%20instead%20of%20working%20out%20a%20bespoke%20rehabilitation%20package%2C%20simply%20puts%20the%20stressed%20assets%20up%20for%20sale.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20the%20way%2C%20as%20instances%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-inside-the-companys-growth-machine%5C%22%3EKrishnapatnam%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-the-inorganic-strategy-behind-the-purchase-of-gangavaram-port%5C%22%3EGangavaram%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%2C%20the%20group%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20acquisition%20drive%20has%20benefited%20from%20state%20action%20or%20support.%20This%20backing%20comes%20with%20large%20rewards%20for%20the%20group%20%E2%80%93%20but%20also%20risks.%20On%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20it%20accumulates%20assets%20rapidly.%20On%20the%20other%2C%20the%20perception%20of%20what%20Sharmila%20Gopinath%20of%20the%20Asian%20Corporate%20Governance%20Association%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F02%2F04%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-modi-india.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecalls%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Elock%20step%20between%20the%20government%20and%20Adani%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%