The%20decision%20was%20decried%20by%20critics%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20monopolise%20traffic%20in%20these%20large%20vessels.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Gangavaram%20itself%2C%20Adani%20is%20facing%20complaints%20about%20the%20abuse%20of%20market%20position%20%E2%80%93%20like%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftelanganatoday.com%2Fvizag-steel-plant-forced-to-pay-additional-rs-60-cr-annually-for-raw-materials%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehike%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20its%20coal%20tariffs%20for%20the%20Vizag%20Steel%20Plant%2C%20with%20predictable%20impacts%20on%20the%20bottom%20line%20of%20the%20state-owned%20steel%20maker.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECoal%20importers%20who%20baulk%20at%20the%20terms%20set%20for%20using%20Gangavaram%20can%20only%20use%20the%20Vizag%20port%20now.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20fear%20is%20that%20%5Bsomeone%5D%20will%20next%20use%20the%20fear%20of%20pollution%20to%20shut%20down%20coal%20handling%20at%20Vizag%20port%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20small%20coal%20importing%20firm%20in%20Vizag.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20with%20coal%20stocks%20at%20Gangavaram%20rising%20steeply%2C%20locals%20in%20Gangavaram%20village%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20about%20heightened%20pollution%2C%20breathing%20trouble%20and%20are%20now%20demanding%20that%20the%20government%20relocate%20their%20village.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20asked%20Adani%20to%20comment%20on%20these%20allegations.%20In%20its%20emailed%20response%2C%20however%2C%20the%20company%20didn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Et%20answer%20the%20question.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20other%20costs%20and%20consequences%20too.%20Once%20Adani%20acquired%20Krishnapatnam%20in%202020%2C%20large%20users%20of%20the%20port%20