seller%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20report%20adds%20another%20complication%20as%20well.%20If%20Adani%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20cash%20crunch%20worsens%20%E2%80%93%20and%20he%20is%20compelled%20to%20sell%20some%20of%20these%20concessions%20%E2%80%93%20there%20is%20no%20telling%20who%20might%20pick%20up%20critical%20Indian%20infrastructure%20like%20ports.%20As%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EForbes%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fgautam-adanis-brother-behind-undisclosed-pledging-of-adani-shares-to-russian-bank-for-loan-forbes%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20recently%2C%20Vinod%20Adani%20had%20pledged%20shares%20with%20Russia%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20tainted%20VTB%20Bank.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20then%2C%20there%20is%20the%20political%20economy%20question%20of%20cronyism%2C%20both%20at%20the%20national%20and%20state%20levels.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20a%20sea%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20head%20of%20an%20Andhra%20Pradesh-based%20renewables%20company.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ECompanies%20are%20being%20forced%20to%20%5Bexit%5D.%20This%20has%20especially%20picked%20up%20since%20the%202019%20election.%E2%80%9D%20Like%20many%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20spoke%20with%20for%20this%20story%2C%20he%20did%20not%20want%20to%20be%20identified.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20governments%20have%20doled%20out%20favours%20to%20preferred%20companies.%20We%20are%20now%20seeing%20something%20new.%20The%20charge%20now%20being%20made%20by%20businessmen%20and%20the%20opposition%20is%20that%20ruling%20parties%20are%20helping%20their%20preferred%20firms%20annex%20their%20peers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20them%2C%20this%20represents%20a%20malign%20evolution%20in%20the%20use%20of%20political%20power%20in%20India%20%E2%80%93%20and%20transcends%20existing%20definitions%20of%20crony%20capitalism.%20This%20also%20suggests%20that%20the%20problem%20is%20not%20of%20help%20being%20given%20to%20just%20one%20or%20two%20corporate%20groups.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20will%20see%20many%20more%20large%20acquisitions%20backed%20by%20political%20parties%20in%20the%20next%2010%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20former%20member%20of%20the%20state%20planning%20board%20for%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20social%20contract%20between%20the%20people%20and%20political%20parties%20comes%20under%20strain%2C%20it%20is%20vital%20that%20institutions%20tasked%20with%20regulating%20the%20corporate%20sector%20do%20the%20job%20they%20are%20supposed%20to.%C2%A0%20So%20far%2C%20however%2C%20there%20is%20little%20sign%20of%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E(M.%20Rajshekhar%20is%20an%20independent%20reporter%20studying%20corruption%2C%20oligarchy%20and%20the%20political%20economy%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20environment.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20author%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.in%2FDespite-State-India-Lets-People%2Fdp%2F8194879019%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20State%3A%20Why%20India%20Lets%20Its%20People%20Down%20and%20How%20They%20Cope%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Reporting%20for%20this%20project%20was%20supported%20by%20Pulitzer%20Center)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAppendix%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAdani%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3Es%20Response%20to%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3Es%20Questionnaire%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2