-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecarrying%20two%20additional%20crew%20members%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20didn't%20know%20they%20were%20being%20flown%20into%20Ukraine%20by%20the%20defecting%20pilot%2C%20Ukrainian%20military%20officials%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.radiosvoboda.org%2Fa%2Fnews-budanov-rozpoviv-jak-vdalosya-vymanyty-pilota-mi-8%2F32561846.html%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0wCsVKCQl-mm0L6CqM6SIXclgX35DChRCDgMy56c0iJGk7e4hSKZtN9nI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERadio%20Free%20Europe%2FRadio%20Liberty.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Ukraine's%20military%20intelligence%20agency%20said%20the%20two%20crew%20members%20tried%20to%20run%20when%20they%20realized%20what%20happened%20and%20were%20ultimately%20unwilling%20to%20surrender%20and%20%26quot%3Beliminated.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussian%20propaganda%20outlets%20said%20the%20helicopter%20landed%20in%20Ukraine%20by%20mistake%20after%20the%20pilot%20became%20disoriented%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Kyiv%20Post%2C%20but%20the%20Poltava%20military%20air%20base%20in%20Kharkiv%20where%20the%20helicopter%20landed%20is%20more%20than%20180%20miles%20from%20the%20frontline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20led%20to%20the%20defection%2C%20Ukraine%20undoubtedly%20secured%20itself%20a%20propaganda%20win%2C%20Ryan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Ukrainians%20can%20use%20this%20to%20set%20an%20example%20for%20other%20Russians%20who%20might%20like%20to%20defect%20or%20not%20fight%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20incident%20plays%20in%20Ukraine's%20favor%20among%20a%20Russian%20domestic%20audience%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-russian-defectors-pilot-mi-8-helicopter-jet-parts-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693015476000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e951bbbc26b40019905e86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%