C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20anti-personnel%20land%20mines%20in%20war%20was%20banned%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdisarmament.unoda.org%2Fconvarms%2Flandmines%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAnti%252Dpersonnel%2520landmines%2520are%2520prohibited%2Ccountries%2520have%2520joined%2520this%2520treaty.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E1997%20Mine%20Ban%20Convention%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Despite%20having%20signed%20the%20treaty%2C%20Ukraine%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20Human%20Rights%20Watch%20of%20using%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuman-rights-watch-tells-ukraine-investigate-use-of-banned-mines-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebanned%20%26quot%3Bbutterfly%26quot%3B%20mines%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Russia.%20Russia%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20never%20signed%20on%20to%20the%20treaty%2C%20nor%20has%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20war%20ended%20tomorrow%2C%20it%20would%20take%20years%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-ukraine-uses-thermal-imaging-drones-to-find-russia-mines-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etedious%2C%20dangerous%20work%20to%20clear%20the%20minefields%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20longer%20it%20drags%20on%2C%20the%20worse%20the%20situation%20gets.%20Epstein%20said%20that%20the%20mines%20are%20only%20going%20to%20get%20more%20and%20more%20buried%20under%20dirt%20and%20snow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20a%20city%20is%20liberated%2C%20it%20will%20take%20a%20very%20long%20time%20to%20just%20make%20it%20so%20it's%20really%20safe%20to%20live%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20For%20all%20the%20towns%2C%20fields%2C%20and%20farmlands%20where%20mines%20have%20potentially%20been%20laid%2C%20he%20said%20there%20will%20also%20be%20a%20difficult%20question%20to%20answer%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20deep%20do%20we%20need%20to%20scrape%20the%20surface%20of%20the%20Earth%20to%20really%20make%20these%20places%20safe%20to%20live%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20could%20be%20several%20years%20before%20the%20mine-clearing%20operations%20make%20it%20safe%20in%20some%20areas%20of%20Ukraine.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20even%20scraping%20away%20the%20top%20three%20feet%20of%20dirt%20might%20not%20be%20enough%20to%20feel%20safe%2C%20he%20said.%20What%20if%20the%20mines%20are%20now%20buried%20six%20feet%20underground%3F%20Or%20eight%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228368%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20soldier%20with%20a%20prosthetic%20leg%20is%20assisted%20inw%20alking%20by%20a%20physical%20therapist%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e9144cb413420019a3d88b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225584%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESerhii%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20soldier%20who%20lost%20a%20leg%20from%20a%20land%20mine%20while%20fighting%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20is%20assisted%20by%20Rebecca%20Gonzalez%20at%20the%20physical%20therapy%20department%20at%20Staten%20Island%20University%20Hospital%20on%20July%2021%2C%202023%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20The%20soldier%2C%20who%20is%20preparing%20to%20return%20to%20the%20war%20against%20Russia%2C%20was%20brought%20to%20New%20York%20through%20a%20program%20with%20the%20non-profit%20Kind%20Deeds.%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Platt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20long-term%20issue%20mines%20pose%20for%20Ukraine%20is%20the%20care%20that's%20going%20to%20be%20required%20for%20those%20who%20have%20been%20injured.%20Between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famputations-ukraine-levels-not-seen-since-world-war-i-report-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E20%2C000%20to%2050%2C000%20Ukrainians%20are%20estimated%20to%20have%20had%20an%20amputation%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20Russia%20invaded%2C%20reaching%20levels%20not%20seen%20since%20World%20War%20I%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal.%20While%20Epstein%20said%20Ukraine%20has%20a%20good%20medical%20system%2C%20the%20de