%20sunglasses%20backwards%20on%20his%20head%20looks%20at%20a%20receipt%20while%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20shopping%20cart%20at%20a%20Giant%20grocery%20store%20in%20Washington%20DC%20in%202020.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F644003a4632fda001803a08b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224070%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EInstacart%20has%20gotten%20its%20shoppers%20to%20deliver%20more%20orders%20at%20a%20time%20for%20the%20same%20or%20less%20pay%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3Cp%3EEvelyn%20Hockstein%2FFor%20The%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EInstacart's%20IPO%20filing%20shows%20the%20company%20booked%20a%20profit%20in%202022.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20contributor%20was%20a%2050%25%20increase%20in%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3Bbatch%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20the%20number%20of%20orders%20shopped%20at%20once.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShoppers%20have%20told%20Insider%20that%20batching%20has%20led%20them%20to%20do%20more%20work%20for%20the%20same%20pay.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-files-prospectus-with-sec-ahead-of-ipo-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInstacart's%20IPO%20filing%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%20the%20company%20turned%20a%20profit%20last%20year.%20An%20increase%20in%20productivity%20by%20its%20gig%20workers%20contributed%20to%20that%20profit.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202019%2C%20Instacart%20has%20increased%20its%20%26quot%3Bbatch%20rate%2C%26quot%3B%20or%20the%20average%20number%20of%20orders%20shopped%20and%20delivered%20in%20a%20single%20trip%2C%20by%2050%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20filing.%20Instead%20of%20having%20one%20shopper%20fill%20a%20single%20order%20at%20a%20time%2C%20Instacart%20has%20pushed%20its%20gig%20workers%20to%20shop%20and%20deliver%20multiple%20orders%20at%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20one%20of%20the%20factors%20that%20helped%20the%20company%20turn%20a%20profit%20last%20year.%20In%202021%2C%20Instacart%20booked%20a%20net%20loss%20of%20%2473%20million%2C%20according%20to%20the%20prospectus%20it%20filed%20with%20the%20SEC.%20In%202022%2C%20it%20reported%20a%20profit%20of%20%24428%20million.%20Other%20factors%2C%20such%20as%20its%20growing%20advertising%20business%2C%20also%20factored%20into%20the%20company's%20profitability.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20drive%20efficiencies%20through%20the%20number%20of%20orders%20powered%20by%20technology-backed%20picking%20and%20batching%20abilities%20that%20help%20shoppers%20fulfill%20multiple%20orders%20simultaneously%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20section%20of%20the%20prospectus%20titled%20%26quot%3BEconomies%20of%20Scale%26quot%3B%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20practice%20of%20batching%20helps%20efficiency%20%26quot%3Bby%20reducing%20the%20cost%20and%20time%20to%20fulfill%20each%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20section%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFilling%20multiple%20orders%20at%20once%20has%20become%20a%20feature%20of%20shopping%20for%20Instacart%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20that%20shoppers%20say%20has%20weighed%20on%20their%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstacart%20frequently%20batches%20two%20or%20three%20orders%20together.%20Shoppers%20have%20to%20accept%20all%20of%20the%20orders%20in%20a%20batch%20to%20shop%20them%20and%20receive%20their%20pay%2C%20several%20Instacart%20workers%20have%20told%20Insider%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20shoppers%20who%20have%20worked%20for%20Instacart%20for%20several%20years%20have%20told%20Insider%20that%20their%20pay%20per%20order%20has%20decreased%20since%20batching%20became%20widespread.%20One%20Instacart%20shopper%20in%20Utah%20told%20Insider%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-shoppers-wait-in-parking-lots-to-claim-orders-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree-order%20batches%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%