very%20year%2C%20each%20one%20boasting%20more%20power%20and%20features%20than%20the%20last%2C%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-gaming-pc%5C%22%3Ebest%20gaming%20PCs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20defined%20by%20the%20performance%20of%20their%20graphics%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20your%20PC%20is%20more%20than%20a%20couple%20years%20old%2C%20and%20you've%20already%20upgraded%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-ssd%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolid-state%20drive%20(SSD)%3C%2Fa%3E%20rather%20than%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-a-hard-drive%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehard%20disk%20drive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20upgrading%20your%20graphics%20card%20is%20likely%20the%20best%20way%20to%20improve%20your%20computer's%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstalling%20a%20graphics%20card%20isn't%20difficult%2C%20but%20it%20requires%20opening%20your%20computer%20case%20and%20replacing%20components%2C%20so%20it%20might%20seem%20daunting%20if%20you've%20never%20tinkered%20inside%20your%20computer%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20step-by-step%20guide%20to%20replacing%20your%20graphics%20card.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMake%20sure%20your%20new%20graphics%20card%20is%20compatible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGraphics%20cards%20aren't%20one-size-fits-all%2C%20and%20the%20more%20powerful%20the%20card%2C%20the%20more%20resources%20it'll%20draw%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20computer.%20Make%20sure%20your%20new%20card%20will%20fit%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20setup%20before%20you%20buy%2C%20or%20you%20might%20end%20up%20needing%20to%20get%20a%20refund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20usually%20four%20main%20considerations%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20your%20power%20supply%20unit%20(PSU)%20large%20enough%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Many%20graphics%20cards%20require%20that%20your%20computer's%20power%20supply%20deliver%20500%20watts%20or%20more.%20Check%20the%20specs%20that%20came%20with%20your%20computer%20or%20look%20at%20the%20ID%20sticker%20on%20the%20power%20supply%20itself.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20there%20enough%20power%20connectors%20for%20your%20new%20graphics%20card%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Newer%20graphics%20cards%20need%20more%20power%20than%20older%20models%2C%20so%20you%20may%20need%20to%20connect%20anywhere%20from%20one%20to%20three%208-pin%20power%20connectors%20from%20your%20power%20supply.%20Again%2C%20check%20the%20specs%20of%20your%20PSU%20and%20graphics%20card%20to%20make%20sure%20they're%20compatible.%20Modular%20power%20supply%20units%20can%20easily%20add%20additional%20power%20connectors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EIs%20your%20CPU%20fast%20enough%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Your%20computer's%20CPU%20is%20the%20piece%20that%20handles%20the%20computer's%20most%20basic%20functions.%20If%20your%20CPU%20is%20too%20old%2C%20even%20the%20most%20advanced%20graphics%20card%20in%20the%20world%20won't%20improve%20your%20computer's%20performance%2C%20it'll%20create%20a%20bottleneck%20that%20slows%20your%20computer%20down.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20the%20card%20physically%20fit%20in%20the%20computer%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20new%20graphics%20card%20may%20require%20more%20than%20one%20PCI%20Express%20expansion%20slot.%20And%20length%20might%20be%20an%20issue%3A%20Not%20all%20card%20slots%20are%20%26quot%3Bfull%20length%2C%26quot%3B%20so%20you'll%20need%20to%20make%20sure%20there's%20room%20on%20the%20motherboard%2C%20as%20well%20as%20enough%20space%20in%20your%20case%20for%20a%20larger%20card.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How_to_install_a_graphics_card%201%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F601461ee6dfbe10018e00d19%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22848%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20full-length%20graphics%20card%20like%20this%20one%20might%20not%20fit%20in%20a%20smaller%20computer%20chassis.%3Cp%3EDave%20Johnson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20uninstall%20the%20old%20graphics%20drivers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20replacing%20a%20graphics%20card%20with%20a%20more%20modern%20version%20in%20the%20same%20family%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20you're%20upgrading%20an%20older%20Nvidia%20card%20to%20a%20newer%20one%20%E2%80%94%20then%20you%20can%20skip%20this%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20you're%20switching%20from%20AMD%20to%20Nvidia%2C%20or%20vice%20versa%2C%20then%20you%20should%20uninstall%20your%20old%20graphics%20drivers%20before%20starting%20the%20new%20installation.%20You%20can%20use%20the%20Settings%20app%20in%20Windows%20to%20remove%20your%20Nvidia%20GeForce%20or%20AMD%20Catalyst%20software%20%E2%80%94%20check%20out%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-uninstall-programs-on-windows-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20article%20on%20how%20to%20properly%20uninstall%20programs%20on%20Windows%2010%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20information.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20install%20the%20new%20graphics%20card%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20you'll%20only%20need%20one%20tool%20for%20this%20job%3A%20a%20small%20Phillips%20head%20screwdriver.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Completely%20turn%20off%20your%20computer%20by%20clicking%20the%20Start%20button%2C%20then%20%26quot%3BPower%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BShut%20Down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Remove%20the%20computer's%20side%20panel%20(it%20might%20be%20a%20tool-less%20case%2C%20or%20you%20may%20need%20to%20unscrew%20the%20panel).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How_to_install_a_graphics_card%203%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60146371a7c0c4001991def3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERemove%20the%20side%20panel%20to%20get%20to%20the%20graphics%20card%20slot%20%E2%80%94%20you%20may%20need%20to%20remove%20one%20or%20two%20screws.%3Cp%3EDave%20Johnson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Find%20the%20graphics%20card.%20If%20you%20haven't%20already%2C%20disconnect%20the%20video%20cable%20that%20runs%20to%20the%20monitor.%20Then%20unscrew%20the%20backplate%20holding%20the%20graphics%20card%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How_to_install_a_graphics_card%204%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60146412a7c0c4001991def9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERemove%20the%20screws%20holding%20the%20graphics%20card's%20backplate%20in%20place.%3Cp%3EDave%20Johnson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20graphics%20card%20is%20held%20down%20by%20a%20clip%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20PCI%20Express%20card%20slot.%20Unlock%20the%20clip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221505%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22How_to_install_a_graphics_card%205%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60146e81d6c5e60019c6e046%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221003%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYou'll%20need%20to%20carefully%20unlatch%20the%20clip%20holding%20the%20card%20in%20the%20PCI%20Express%20slot.%3Cp%3EDave%20Johnson%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Gently%20rocking%20the%20card%2C%20remove%20the%20graphics%20card%20from%20the%20slot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Take%20the%20new%20graphics%20card%20and%2C%20positioning%20it