mlas-demanding-separate-administration-denies-division-of-manipur-101692903840763.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20reported%20Singh%20as%20saying%20that%20he%20had%20been%20in%20%E2%80%98regular%E2%80%99%20touch%20with%20the%2010%20Kuki-Zo-Hmar%20MLAs%20who%20have%20been%20demanding%20separate%20administration%20for%20hill%20districts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20told%20the%20MLAs%20that%20I%20will%20provide%20them%20with%20security%20and%20that%20we%20must%20work%20together%20to%20restore%20normalcy.%20I%20have%20also%20spoken%20to%20the%20civil%20society%20organisations%20in%20Imphal%20(Meitei%20groups)%20and%20said%20that%20the%20MLAs%20should%20not%20be%20stopped%20from%20visiting%20the%20valley%20(Imphal)%20for%20work.%20The%20MLAs%20must%20join%20work%20immediately.%20Also%2C%20let%20me%20reiterate%20there%20can%20be%20no%20division%20of%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20chief%20minister%20had%20told%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20claims%2C%20the%2010%20tribal%20legislators%20alleged%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20claim%20might%20be%20%E2%80%9Ca%20ploy%20to%20sow%20seeds%20of%20mistrust%20between%20them%20and%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20hereby%20clarified%20by%20all%20the%2010%20Kuki-Zomi-Hmar%20MLAs%20that%20we%20have%20not%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20CM%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20since%20the%20outbreak%20of%20the%20communal%20violence%20(in%20Manipur)%20in%20May%202023%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20legislators%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20those%20who%20signed%20the%20statement%20seven%20of%20them%20belong%20to%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20two%20from%20the%20Kuki%20People%E2%80%99s%20Alliance%20(KPA)%2C%20and%20the%20other%20MLA%20is%20an%20Independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislators%20recounted%20the%20violent%20attack%20on%20their%20fellow%20MLA%20Vungzagin%20Valte%20on%20May%204%2C%20a%20day%20after%20violence%20began%20in%20the%20state.%20Valte%20%E2%80%93%20a%20BJP%20MLA%20and%20adviser%20to%20chief%20minister%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20had%20been%20admitted%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20critical%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlleging%20that%20there%20has%20been%20no%20inquiry%20or%20arrest%20in%20the%20case%20so%20far%2C%20the%20tribal%20legislators%20said%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20%E2%80%9Cface%E2%80%9D%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfate%E2%80%9D%20of%20their%20colleague%20by%20going%20to%20the%20valley.%20%E2%80%9COf%20late%2C%20Imphal%20had%20become%20the%20%E2%80%98Valley%20of%20Death%E2%80%99%20for%20Kuki-Zo-Hmar%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20legislators%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Valte%20had%20been%20brutally%20attacked%20in%20the%20state%20capital%20while%20he%20was%20returning%20from%20a%20meeting%20from%20the%20official%20bungalow%20of%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20asserting%20that%20they%20have%20no%20intention%20to%20communicate%20with%20Singh%2C%20they%20reiterated%20their%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20chief%20secretary%20and%20police%20chief%20for%20the%20Hill%20Districts%20as%20a%20temporary%20measure%20until%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20political%20dialogue%20of%20SoO%20groups%2FKNO-UPF%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20They%20had%20also%20demanded%20the%20same%20in%20the%20memorandum%20they%20submitted%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20August%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MLAs%20also%20urged%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20accept%20their%20%E2%80%9Clegitimate%20demand%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20separate%20administration%20within%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20constitution%20to%20restore%20permanent%20peace%20and%20settlement%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692979315000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30163218%2FFwqAt6VXsAIGp1_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthew